OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776125001
OL,3,CRetail sales 'tepid' as Middle East
OL,4,Cconflict raises consumer caution
OL,6,FSales of consumer goods other than
OL,7,Ffood were "tepid" in March amid
OL,8,Fheightened caution among shoppers due
OL,9,Fto the Middle East conflict, figures
OL,10,Fshow.
OL,12,FNon-food sales increased by 0.9% year
OL,13,Fon year last month, below the 12-month
OL,14,Faverage of 1.1%, according to the
OL,15,FBritish Retail Consortium (BRC) and
OL,16,FKPMG.
OL,26,@oD@KOUoD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
