CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776125001
OL,3,CRetail sales 'tepid' as Middle East
OL,4,Cconflict raises consumer caution
OL,6,FSeparate figures from Barclays show
OL,7,Ftravel spending declined by 3.3% in
OL,8,FMarch after five years of growth as
OL,9,Ftrips abroad were delayed or swapped
OL,10,Ffor staycations.
OL,12,FConsumer card spending increased 0.9%
OL,13,Fyear on year, down from February's 1%,
OL,14,Fthe bank's data shows.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
