FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776125001
OL,3,CRetail sales 'tepid' as Middle East
OL,4,Cconflict raises consumer caution
OL,6,FEssential spending returned to growth
OL,7,F` up 0.5% ` for the first time since
OL,8,FJuly last year as fuel prices surged,
OL,9,Fwhile discretionary spending growth
OL,10,Fslowed to 1.1%, driven by the decline
OL,11,Fin travel, for the first time since
OL,12,F2021.
OL,14,FHowever, a survey for Barclays found
OL,15,Foverall consumer resilience remained
OL,16,Fstrong, with 71% of UK adults feeling
OL,17,Fconfident in their ability to live
OL,18,Fwithin their means each month.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
