FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776125001
OL,3,CRetail sales 'tepid' as Middle East
OL,4,Cconflict raises consumer caution
OL,6,FIn response to uncertainty around the
OL,7,FMiddle East conflict, 14% said they
OL,8,Fwere delaying major purchases or
OL,9,Ffinancial decisions, while the same
OL,10,Fproportion were building up a savings
OL,11,Fbuffer in case costs rise.
OL,13,FSome 74% anticipate ongoing tensions
OL,14,Fwill continue to affect the cost of
OL,15,Fliving throughout the rest of the year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776125001
OL,3,CRetail sales 'tepid' as Middle East
OL,4,Cconflict raises consumer caution
OL,6,FJack Meaning, chief UK economist at
OL,7,FBarclays, said: "Shoppers delaying
OL,8,Fmajor purchases and building up a
OL,9,Fsavings buffer in response to the
OL,10,Fshock from the Middle East reinforces
OL,11,Four view that activity will be muted
OL,12,Fin the coming months.
OL,14,F"With an interest rate decision due in
OL,15,Fless than three weeks' time, the Bank
OL,16,Fof England will need to consider how
OL,17,Fto balance this softening economy with
OL,18,Fthe inflation already taking effect.
OL,26,@oD@QOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1776125001
OL,3,CRetail sales 'tepid' as Middle East
OL,4,Cconflict raises consumer caution
OL,6,F"Our modelling suggests this balance
OL,7,Fis best struck by holding rates,
OL,8,Fcontaining the worst of inflation
OL,9,Fwithout unduly squeezing consumers."
OL,11,FOpinium surveyed 2,000 UK adults
OL,12,Fbetween March 27-31.
